title: Myra Breckinridge (1970)
description:
MYRA BRECKINRIDGE (1970)
Directed by Michael Sarne
Based on a novel by Gore Vidal

Starring Raquel Welch, Mae West, John Huston, Farrah Fawcett, Rex Reed

Notorious X-rated transgressive satire / comedy based on a viciously funny novel by Gore Vidal about a movie critic who undergoes a sex change.  Sullen Rex Reed becomes ultra-glamorous Raquel Welch who sets out to teach America a lesson about the true nature of the sexes. 

It's crazy.

This is the "Special Edition" of the film released on DVD in America in 2004.
